  "texts": [
    "Radiological data has been combined with other data types for predictive AI systems in various clinical disciplines like oncology [21] [22] [23] [24] or neurology 25, 26.",
    "For a systematic review of studies on the fusion of medical imaging and electronic health record (EHR) data using deep learning, we refer the reader to Huang et al.",
    "Yet oftentimes, different research groups investigate similar questions with variable approaches and differing results.",
    "For example, the prediction of Mild Cognitive Impairment or Alzheimer's disease based on the ADNI dataset is frequently investigated [27] [28] [29] [30] [31] [32].",
    "But their predictive accuracy varies, and many studies do not discuss which input modalities or features contributed most to the prediction."
